erforms the traditional single-stage (without decomposition)\nsolution approach in both convergence capability and computational efficiency.\nThe feasibility performance of the proposed stochastic SOC-ACOPF model is also\ndemonstrated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Aug 2021 19:24:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
