nstraints from cosmological observations. We\nalso present a new design of an emulator of the non-linear power spectrum whose\npredictions can be adapted to an arbitrary choice of evolution parameters and\nredshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Aug 2021 22:01:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 08:57:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
