aws or exponential functions, -- is also\ncarried out. An empirical experiment on a large dataset of Italian companies\nvalidates the theoretical framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Aug 2021 15:07:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-10"}
